# [8] Bus-routed CLI dispatch: STILL blocked on 0.9.4, now with a precise root
#     cause — the current kernel's topic delivery is subscribe-driven (Rust-SDK
#     capsules like astrid-capsule-cli declare [subscribe] and receive topics),
#     but the published JS SDK 0.1.0 predates that interface: with the CLI
#     proxy installed, the correct provider topic (cli.v1.command.run.arcade-player,
#     astrid#891) and a [subscribe] entry declared, the JS capsule's interceptor
#     hook never fires (entry log never appears; dispatch times out after 70s).
#     Full write-up: patches/UPSTREAM.md.

