# Key delivery note: on astrid 0.9.4 the entire config surface returns none to
# JS capsules — get-config sees neither [env] defaults, nor `astrid capsule
# config --set` values, nor even the kernel's own ASTRID_SOCKET_PATH builtin
# (probe line above: "GEMINI_API_KEY unset, ASTRID_SOCKET_PATH unset"). The
# key therefore rides in the LOCALLY-BUILT wasm (gen-local-key.mjs, gitignored;
# target/ never committed), with runtime config tried first so newer kernels
# take over automatically. Full write-up: patches/UPSTREAM.md finding 4.

